        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            5
          ],
          1,
          "spearheaded in Congress by Biden"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " and the lending industry."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "Biden‚Äôs student debt cancellation plan is now under attack by Republicans, who are preparing legal challenges to stop the move, "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            6,
            0
          ],
          1,
          "The Washington Post"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          1,
          " reported"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " Thursday. If one of these lawsuits is successful, bankruptcy reform could become even more crucial for relieving debtors of their burdens."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
