      "h3",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "A Battle Over ‚ÄòUndue Hardship‚Äô"
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "Thanks in part to laws that Biden supported as a senator and Warren fought as a law professor, it is much more difficult to secure bankruptcy protections for student debt than for any other kind of debt. Unlike other debtors, student borrowers must prove they face ‚Äúundue hardship‚Äù in order to have their debts reduced or erased."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
